    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Type of elaborate wheelchairs, sometimes glassed, especially those made in England in the mid-19th century and used at spas and seaside resorts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
